b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.24-26?lang=por#p24\">3 Né. 5:24–26</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note5c\" data-full-marker=\"5c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124136443\" id=\"note5c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.9?lang=por#p9\">1 Né. 22:9</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.26-29?lang=por#p26\">3 Né. 21:26–29</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124136444\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.30-42?lang=por#p30\">1 Né. 13:30–42</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.3?lang=por#p3\">2 Né. 30:3</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note6b\" data-full-marker=\"6b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124136445\" id=\"note6b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.5?lang=por#p5\">2 Né. 32:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.32,35-36?lang=por#p32\">3 Né. 11:32, 35–36</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/holy-ghost?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Espírito Santo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124136446\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/restoration-of-the-gospel?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Restauração do Evangelho</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124136447\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.14?lang=por#p14\">1 Né. 13:14</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.9,15?lang=por#p9\">Mó